    Description
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model
    Provides an overlay of the Metaschema module model (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model) using bound Java class annotations (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations) to represent module constructs annotated on Java classes.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations
    Provides a set of annotations for associating Module information with a Java class.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.metaschema
    Provides an implementation of the Module model (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model) represented by a module-specific set of bound Java classes (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.metaschema.binding).
